python PEP8:
python Enhancement proposal:PEP8 is a style guide fro python code.writing code with good logic is crucial
in programming,but many other aspects makes quality of the  code readable and consistent. 
INDENTATION:In python, unlike other programming languages,indentation is utilized to define code blocks.
The level of lines of code is determined by indentation  which are an important feature of programming 
language.
NAMING CONVENTION: To make the programm less dificult and more readable a few naming standards should
be observed.
single lowercase     n = 2
single uppercase     N = 2
lowercase            num = 2
lowercase with underscore  input_number = 2
uppercase    NUM = 2
uppercase with underscore INPUT_NUMBER = 2
